{"Title":"菜心粥的做法","Primary":["大米100克","油菜苔500克","姜10克"],"Auxiliary":["食用油10克","盐1勺"],"Flavoring":[],"Setups":["1.先洗米","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267529955854.jpg","2.然后放入适量的清水浸泡1小时","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267569114152.jpg","3.往锅内放入少许的食用油","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267540175716.jpg","4.接着才开大火煲粥，记得不要盖盖子哦","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267571231436.jpg","5.当锅内的粥在沸腾时，把火关到中火继续煲","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267574356048.jpg","6.全程开着中火煲粥，看，锅内的粥虽然是在沸腾，但却不会淤出来哦","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267577343281.jpg","7.这时准备迟菜心","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267579510028.jpg","8.洗净后切小粒，把姜切细丝","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267580809450.jpg","9.当粥煲至绵软时，把菜心粒放入","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267582173672.jpg","10.接着放入姜丝","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267583677735.jpg","11.加入适量的盐调味","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267584836283.jpg","12.欧了，一款清淡爽口的粥水就做好啦","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267586391583.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267530404988.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267532573976.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267535925740.jpg","[image]:http://site.meishij.net/rs/72/122/2343072/n2343072_142267539069913.jpg","烹饪技巧","因是素食粥，所以在熬粥的时候，适当地放少许的油，会让粥品喝起来更润滑些。"]}